e who &quot;see&quot; Devatas. Such a=\r\nn interaction can very good, to just another day with nothing special. It a=\r\nll depends on how much internal preparation has been done by the seeker. As=\r\n an analogy, you can, if lucky, go and meet Barrack Obama say hi and come b=\r\nack. Nothing much happens. Over time you forget it and life goes on. Or you=\r\n can also meet Obama and then maybe impress him so much that he in turn doe=\r\ns something really nice for you which he is well capable of, which sustains=\r\n long and changes your life. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Then there is the causal form and the =\r\ngreater causal form. These are too rare. To have a &quot;Darshan&quot;/experience of\n=\r\n a Devata in these forms, one will have to do solid work of self-transforma=\r\ntion. That is detachment, control of internal enemies, etc etc, the standar=\r\nd advices which all scriptures and sadgurus tell us. One experience of any =\r\nDevata in the causal form is sufficient to leave a massive impact on a pers=\r\non&#39;s life for ever. And the greater causal is mostly offlimits for just abo=\r\nut 99.999999% of us. That is the Universal Form. These are similar to exper=\r\nience of the Self or the soul, as enumerated in the Upanishadic literature.=\r\n Nothing less.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-Regards&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;Rajarshi&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=3D=\r\n&quot;yiv4905100129yui_3_7_2_43_1376280893069_58&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=3D&quot;yiv4905100129yu=\r\ni_3_7_2_43_1376280893069_69&quot; style=3D&quot;font-family:times new roman, new york=\r\n, times, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=3D&quot;yiv4905100129yui_3_7_2_43_1376=\r\n280893069_60&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;div class=3D&quot;yiv4905100129MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=3D&quot;yi=\r\nv4905100129yui_3_7_2_43_1376280893069_70&quot; style=3D&quot;font-family:times new ro=\r\nman,\n new york, times, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class=3D&quot;yiv4905100129Apple-st